subject: ATTENTION: Beneficiary.
body:
ATTENTION: Beneficiary.
I am writing to inform you that your compensation/winning payment was
approved today by the Board and Directors of United Nation Committee
on Rewards and Compensation.
You are therefore advised to reconfirm your details to enable the
financial department release your payment to you without any delay.
Thus, reconfirm the following:
1. Your Full Name:
2. Your residential address:
3. Your direct phone number:
4. Occupation
We look forward to your prompt response.
Thank you.
Mr Larry Dillon
Contact Email: 
ld09682400@gmail.com
Director of Payments,
United Nations Ministry of Foreign Affairs

subject: Re: ATTENTION: Beneficiary.
body:
Dear Mr. Larry Dillon,

Thank you for your email. I am excited to hear about the approval of my winning payment by the United Nations Committee on Rewards. Here are the details you requested:

Full Name: Eliza Dane
Address: 123 Main Street, Sydney, NSW 2000, Australia

Best wishes,
